title: Brie, Sausage, Caramelized Apple and Onion Flatbreads with Fig-Mustard Drizzle
description: Brie and caramelized apples are a match made in heaven! This flatbread showcases ooey-gooey Brie cheese, caramelized apples and onions and sausage, all generously drizzled with a delicious fig-mustard sauce. Voila, the perfect sweet and savoury meal to end your day.
